property.value:
A track heavy with strings & textural synths. Useful for major scenes of devestation and defeat (or fear of such), or alternatively of great power and reverence. Big battles, big armies, big supernatural powers, big sacrifices.
The beats don't make full sense here, so don't trust them too much. As a result, sometimes the better way to end the piece is with a fade-out (To End) rather than a deliberate Outro (To Outro).
